action.description: Launch the Clock app using the search function.
Tap the "+" button to start creating a new alarm.
Tap on "12" to set the alarm hour to 12 PM.
Tap on "30" to set the alarm minutes to 30.
Wait for the "OK" button to become enabled, then tap it to confirm the time setting.
Tap on the "Vibrate" option to disable it.
Tap on the "Sunday" button to select it for the alarm.
Tap on the "Friday" button to select it for the alarm.

action.description: Open the app drawer to search for the Clock app.
Tap on the Clock app icon to open the Clock application.
Tap on "Add alarm" to start creating a new alarm.
Select "12" from the hour picker to set the alarm hour.
Tap on the "30" minute mark to set the alarm minutes to 30.
Tap on the OK button to confirm the alarm time.
Tap on the "Sunday" button to select it for the alarm.
Tap on the "Friday" button to select it for the alarm.
Tap on the "Vibrate" toggle to disable vibration for the alarm.
